Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Resembles Sasuke, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess there's\N{\i1}a small resemblance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He kind of talks like...him too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't stare at me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pound you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You tick me off with\Neverything you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't resemble Sasuke at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to portray myself\Nlike that kind of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Portray yourself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you {\i1}do{\i0}  mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't do at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You really tick me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! Don't act like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of your captain, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kakashi taught you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that trust and teamwork\Nare most important to a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on the same team\Nas the great Kakashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a member of Team Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The other member of\Nour Team Kakashi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was just chosen to\Ncover the loss of Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't acknowledge him\Nas a team member...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He betrayed the Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and ran off\Nto serve Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be lumped together\Nwith a cockroach along the same lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Teamwork is indeed important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai... Naruto still doesn't know you\Nvery well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So he may have been out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness I've got at least\None kid who's less objectionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:26.43,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(698,642)}The Fake Smile\N\N \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're getting along...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The new Team Kakashi, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not rookies anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're full-fledged Shinobi now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems Naruto and\Nthe new team member Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't really getting along very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And who's fault was it that\Na team member Naruto can't get along with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was added to Team Kakashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I never thought one of\NLord Danzo's subordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,would end up joining their team...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time for excuses!\NGet a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out about Danzo's intentions\Nand Sai's background!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, Shizune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've left the Naruto and Sai matter\Nto Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be able to set things right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,About that Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get the feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura's becoming more and more\N{\i1}like Lady Tsunade these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope she can mediate between\N{\i1}Naruto and Sai all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surely she isn't throwing gas\N{\i1}on the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to...forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked me good...\Nwith your fake smile earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And here you don't even know\Nanything about Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever speak ill about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insult Sasuke again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine... I won't say anything like that\Nin front of you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's another way of using\Na fake smile, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you grin like that\Nafter getting punched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A smile is the best way to get\Nthrough a tough situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a fake smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly enough,\Neveryone gets fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it said in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it doesn't really work\Nif I do it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Four-Pillar Prison Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll really toss you guys into\Nthis cell if you keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time\Nuntil we get to the Tenchi Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we've still got enough time\Nto take a little detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the secret Jutsu that\N{\i1}only the First Hokage could use...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Wood Style Ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How come Captain Yamato\N{\i1}can use the Wood Style Ninjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who the heck is this guy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As your peacemaker,\NI offer you this suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to improve your rapport,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can toss you guys into\Nthis cell for a full day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or we can stay at a hot spring inn\Nfor a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys probably don't really\Nknow me all that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer the kind and gentle approach,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not against controlling you\Nby fear either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, getting naked together\Nlike this is a great way to bond, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His eyes are totally scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's already controlling us\N{\i1}with fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... So you {\i1}do{\i0} have one, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up with all that talk about my dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For crying out loud, Naruto...\N{\i1}You're talking too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault I'm being laughed at...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad that Sakura's pleased, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, let me tell you\Nan interesting story, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When Master Jiraiya was young,\Nthere was one time when he almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke six ribs and both arms,\Nand several of his internal organs ruptured...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Lady Tsunade beat him up\Nreal good with her incredible strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened because\Nhe did what you're now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,attempting to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Sakura would do....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like\Nthings are going to get busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I start preparing your meals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring them right away then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a nice bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be getting out, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful not to stay\Nin the water too long. You'll get dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot, idiot, are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such magnificent food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it sure looks good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say! Say! Captain Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay if we eat all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I start with...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}really{\i0}  is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get food this\Nawesome every mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yamato can stay\Nwith us forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have Kakashi Sensei stay\Nin the hospital a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...when can I eat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For awhile, you'll only\Nget food intravenously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You still can't move your arms\Nand legs freely, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you can move your arms and legs,\Nyou'll go on a liquid diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll still be quite awhile before\Nyou can eat solid food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to...eat something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, normally after dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd want to have a meeting\Nregarding the mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But the reason why we're staying here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is for improvement of your rapport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget about\Nthe serious stuff for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking, Captain Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead we'll definitely have\Na meeting tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be we're going to stay at\Na hot springs inn tomorrow, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, cut me some slack on that one.\NMy wallet won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could it be that\Nyou're paying for this place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,out of your own pocket, Captain Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! You're sure generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's settled! Captain Yamato will be\Nthe captain of Team Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I second that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's nice today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing over there...?
